app-update - Update installed applications

USAGE:
    app-update [app-name...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Update one or more installed applications. If no app names
    are specified, updates all installed applications and the
    install system itself.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-install-step-timeout SECONDS
        Timeout per update step (default: 300)

    -conf-install-max-concurrent-jobs NUM
        Maximum concurrent jobs (default: nproc)

EXAMPLES:
    app-update
    app-update my-app
    app-update app1 app2 app3
